Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:47.35,Default_Top,NTP,0,0,0,,このひろいシーンどこへでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.44,Default_Top,NTP,0,0,0,,RIDE ON THE NEW CHANCE　
