Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OPCN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OPEN THE NEW DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們克服困難 只為尋求答案
